# =============================================================================
# imessageWithContextSelfExperimentation — copy-friendly .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# Used together with the repo root `.gitignore`. If you copy only this folder
# into a new repo, copy these patterns (and README “Git & environment”) there.

# --- Secrets (never commit `.env`; do commit `.env.example`) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/

# --- Local training weights ---
models/
**/tinker_lora_adapter/
**/tinker_lora_sft_adapter/
*.safetensors
*.bin
*.pt
*.pth
*.ckpt

# --- Large text exports (regenerate from Messages) ---
cpt_out.txt
messages_export.txt

# --- `sft_output.json` stays untracked (iMessage text can contain pasted secrets; GitHub blocks push). ---
# (Covered by root `**/sft_output.json`.)

# --- Tinker request/response dumps (large; may echo payloads) ---
**/sft_tinker_api_dump.json

# --- Intentionally NOT listed (tracked in git) ---
# experiment_results/   — scenario JSON, rubrics, manifests, agent logs, base_results/
